ogical phenomena, the mysterious behaviour of many insects and animals, the sudden and unexplainable emergence of pathological and sickly state of mind, sexuality, death.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Italian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aItalian languagexDialectszItalyzAdda River ValleyxLexicology. 0aItalian languagexDialectszItalyzMaira River ValleyxLexicology. 4aAngst. 4aDialektologie. 4aEthnologie. 4aItalienisch. 4aLexikographie. 4aPsycholinguistik. 7aFOREIGN LANGUAGE STUDY / Italian.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2009z9783110219517oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2009z9783110219470oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978348452351740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978348497127140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783484971271423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783484971271/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGAb2009  aZDB-23-DGGb2009  aZDB-23-DLSc2000d2014